## 7. CSS実装例（主要スタイル）

```css
* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: flex-start;
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: #FAF8F5;
}

/* ルートフレーム */
.sp6-terms {
  width: 375px;
  padding: 32px 10px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 40px;
  background: #FAF8F5;
}

/* ページヘッダー */
.page-header {
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 16px;
  align-items: center;
}

.page-title {
  margin: 0;
  color: #1C1C1C;
  font-size: 23px;
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
}

.page-lead {
  margin: 0;
  width: 320px;
  color: #6B6B6B;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.8;
  text-align: center;
}

/* セクション */
.terms-section {
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 16px;
}

.section-title {
  margin: 0;
  color: #1C1C1C;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: -0.3px;
}

/* 情報カード */
.info-card {
  width: 100%;
  background: #FFFFFF;
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid #E8E5E0;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.card-label {
  background: #F5F3F0;
  padding: 7px 5px;
  color: #6B6B6B;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.card-body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

/* 情報行 */
.info-row {
  display: flex;
  padding: 9px 8px;
}

.info-row--border {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #E8E5E0;
}

.info-label {
  width: 100px;
  color: #6B6B6B;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.info-label--wide {
  width: 140px;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.info-value {
  flex: 1;
  color: #1C1C1C;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* 免責事項リスト */
.disclaimer-list {
  padding: 9px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
}

.disclaimer-item {
  margin: 0;
  color: #1C1C1C;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ルールカード */
.rule-card {
  width: 100%;
  background: #FFFFFF;
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid #E8E5E0;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* ルール項目 */
.rule-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 9px;
}

.rule-item--border {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #E8E5E0;
}

/* ルールアイコン */
.rule-icon {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  background: #F5F3F0;
  border-radius: 8px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}

/* ルールコンテンツ */
.rule-content {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2px;
}

.rule-main {
  color: #1C1C1C;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 400;
}

.rule-sub {
  color: #9A9A9A;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* レスポンシブ対応 */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .sp6-terms {
    max-width: 375px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
}
```

