## 8. アイコン実装の詳細

### Lucideアイコン（SVG直接記述）

**moon（月）:**
```html
<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z" fill="#1E3A5F"/>
</svg>
```

**flame（炎）:**
```html
<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <path d="M8.5 14.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 11 12c0-1.38-.5-2-1-3-1.072-2.143-.224-4.054 2-6 .5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5 2 1.6 3 3.5 3 5.5a7 7 0 1 1-14 0c0-1.153.433-2.294 1-3a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5 2.5z" fill="#1E3A5F"/>
</svg>
```

**volume-x（音量ミュート）:**
```html
<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
  <path d="M11 5L6 9H2v6h4l5 4V5z" fill="#1E3A5F"/>
  <line x1="23" y1="9" x2="17" y2="15" stroke="#1E3A5F" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
  <line x1="17" y1="9" x2="23" y2="15" stroke="#1E3A5F" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
</svg>
